            "title": "西班牙盃│馬德里體育會被巴塞隆拿淘汰 祖利安艾華利斯生涯或首次一年無冠",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"馬德里體育會被巴塞隆拿淘汰，祖利安艾華利斯生涯或首次一年無冠。REUTERS\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/059ac27006476b5310c62ffa63243ae5/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250403/_2025040319310225868.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">馬德里體育會被巴塞隆拿淘汰，祖利安艾華利斯生涯或首次一年無冠。REUTERS</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>馬德里體育會在周三西班牙盃4強次回合，作客0:1不敵巴塞隆拿，總比數輸4:5無緣決賽。在最有機會捧盃的賽事出局，馬體會隨時四大皆空，今季來投的阿根廷前鋒祖利安艾華利斯的捧盃命水勢告一段落，職業生涯首次於一年裡面沒有冠軍。\n\n</p><h2>西班牙盃出局 馬體會今季勢無冠</h2>\n<p>首回合激鬥至賽和4:4的馬體會和巴塞，今場就大為收歛，客軍巴塞憑鋒將費倫托利斯於上半場一箭定江山，作客贏1:0，兩回合計險勝5:4晉級決賽，將會與死敵皇家馬德里爭冠。而牀單軍團無緣決賽，由於他們在歐聯同樣已出局，西甲就落後榜首巴塞9分排第3，要後上奪冠的機會渺茫，今屆唯一冠軍希望就是夏天的世界冠軍球會盃，但這是擴軍至32隊後的首屆比賽，加上強手林立，他們要捧盃絕不容易。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"馬體會不敵巴塞隆拿，無緣西班牙盃決賽。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/68798e90e0aa2d3991684a7f109cacd8/2025-04/1_6.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        馬體會不敵巴塞隆拿，無緣西班牙盃決賽。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"馬體會不敵巴塞隆拿，無緣西班牙盃決賽。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0c99527ea5f73d9cae7169db05e00683/2025-04/2_0_2.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        馬體會不敵巴塞隆拿，無緣西班牙盃決賽。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"費倫托利斯(中)為巴塞隆拿一箭定江山。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/20dc079f905f2176a73be35fba5d73c0/2025-04/3_5.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        費倫托利斯(中)為巴塞隆拿一箭定江山。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"費倫托利斯為巴塞隆拿一箭定江山。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e75401aed6275677e68caf2ff32e4996/2025-04/4_7.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        費倫托利斯為巴塞隆拿一箭定江山。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"費倫托利斯(左)為巴塞隆拿一箭定江山。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/537c5ff4242ea5c31f5179ef78916a1d/2025-04/5_6.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        費倫托利斯(左)為巴塞隆拿一箭定江山。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"巴塞隆拿躋身西班牙盃決賽。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1d76aa3af0178f25e522f74108573943/2025-04/6.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        巴塞隆拿躋身西班牙盃決賽。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"巴塞隆拿躋身西班牙盃決賽。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d4c2875c355c91ca30cb00efe68b0dd9/2025-04/7_2.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        巴塞隆拿躋身西班牙盃決賽。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>艾華利斯或生涯首年無冠軍</h2>\n<p>馬體會大有機會四大皆空，對今季來投的鋒將祖利安艾華利斯而言，可謂上錯船。此子由2018年出道至今，每年都總有球會或國家隊錦標落袋，2018至20年，每年都有一冠，分別是南美自由盃、阿根廷盃和阿根廷超級盃；2022年就有世界盃，而2021年有美洲國家盃及阿根甲；2023年更豪取6個冠軍；去年亦有3個錦標落袋，今年如未能取得西甲或世冠盃，就沒有冠軍，是他生涯首次。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"祖利安艾華利斯(左)有機會首次一年無冠。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/039a174776df70c61dd7c96e126d7dad/2025-04/8_2.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        祖利安艾華利斯(左)有機會首次一年無冠。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"祖利安艾華利斯(右)有機會首次一年無冠。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d5cc088c6754f61d992b94b9048e1d88/2025-04/9_0.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        祖利安艾華利斯(右)有機會首次一年無冠。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"祖利安艾華利斯(右)今場努力鑽營，可是沒有入球。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/566d887431c1249905726a3c113aacf8/2025-04/10_0.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        祖利安艾華利斯(右)今場努力鑽營，可是沒有入球。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"祖利安艾華利斯(左)今場努力鑽營，可是沒有入球。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8bacd537f0955af00b5129a32bc2b96e/2025-04/11_0.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        祖利安艾華利斯(左)今場努力鑽營，可是沒有入球。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"祖利安艾華利斯由2018年出道至今，每年都有冠軍。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3b39639942f5d8e122e72623eb614441/2025-04/12.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        祖利安艾華利斯由2018年出道至今，每年都有冠軍。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"祖利安艾華利斯由2018年出道至今，每年都有冠軍。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/660568e8d61bf3217038b865d5bd5c41/2025-04/13.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        祖利安艾華利斯由2018年出道至今，每年都有冠軍。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
