            "title": "俠醫丨劉佩玥帶病上陣死頂開工 自爆演心機女要色誘陳豪丁子朗 郭柏妍為拍游水戲努力減肥",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<div id=\"vdo-player-container\">\n<video class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin\" controls=\"\" id=\"vdo-player\" muted=\"\" playsinline=\"\" poster=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/686e386/0x0/100/none/e63b35d77c7a274b98641607bca8fccd/2025-04/moonnn.jpg\" width=\"100%\">\n<source src=\"https://video.hkhl.hk/803663f3107c71f0b5195114c1ca0102/37b3b8f31b524136a35b64a635fbc7ef-332ebc9d422f9f980f561f5a345165db-ld.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                        Your browser does not support the video tag.\n                    </source></video>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container web\" data-vslot=\"vod_ad\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67ee6fb49387b\"></div>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container mweb\" data-vslot0=\"vod_ad,2\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67ee6fb49387d\"></div>\n</div>\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"俠醫丨劉佩玥帶病上陣死頂開工 自爆演心機女要色誘陳豪丁子朗 郭柏妍為拍游水戲努力減肥\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/e6edce67d437dcf6450980d7481f76c1/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250403/_2025040319145625769.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">俠醫丨劉佩玥帶病上陣死頂開工 自爆演心機女要色誘陳豪丁子朗 郭柏妍為拍游水戲努力減肥</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>劉佩玥（Moon）出席無綫新劇《俠醫》開鏡拜神，見她氣若游絲兼聲沙，她稱近日天氣忽冷忽熱，加上穿短裙拍攝凍親，不想影響拍攝進度死頂開工，會去看中醫針灸。Moon又稱劇中飾演反派很多突破，角色是個心機女不擇手段，愛上陳豪因而為情做壞事。她又指與很多男演員有對手戲，包括陳豪、馬貫東、丁子朗等，並要色誘他們，有大膽戲和性感演出，大爆拍攝時鄭子誠比她更尷尬。\n\n</p><h2>郭柏妍飾演游泳運動員</h2>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field--item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4175761/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"劉佩玥（Moon）、郭柏妍出席無綫新劇《俠醫》開鏡拜神。\" class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d86fb5bcd845bfdeb07e467a43bbafda/2025-04/0L6A2807.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"img_caption\">\n      劉佩玥（Moon）、郭柏妍出席無綫新劇《俠醫》開鏡拜神。\n    </div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field--item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4175762/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"Moon氣若游絲兼聲沙，原來病了！\" class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0f166f412bf1e47a00ec9d52b10d5503/2025-04/0L6A2734.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"img_caption\">\n      Moon氣若游絲兼聲沙，原來病了！\n    </div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field--item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4175763/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"Moon表示不想影響拍攝進度死頂開工，會去看中醫針灸。\" class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7d668b363c9b3b881d58c26c98c9852d/2025-04/0L6A2751.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"img_caption\">\n      Moon表示不想影響拍攝進度死頂開工，會去看中醫針灸。\n    </div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field--item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4175766/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"Moon又說劇中飾演反派很多突破，角色是個心機女不擇手段。\" class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7264170548ae34d4449cf9f2e9fc8b31/2025-04/0L6A2847.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"img_caption\">\n      Moon又說劇中飾演反派很多突破，角色是個心機女不擇手段。\n    </div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field--item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4175767/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"郭柏妍飾演陳豪妹妹，也是一名游泳運動員。\" class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0e8ecd700b603c2543a4e651dbd35bec/2025-04/0L6A2852.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"img_caption\">\n      郭柏妍飾演陳豪妹妹，也是一名游泳運動員。\n    </div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field--item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4175768/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"郭柏妍表示在拍攝游水戲份前要努力減肥。\" class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ee0888100714ab1af39cd6bbc6cc0cb2/2025-04/0L6A2862.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"img_caption\">\n      郭柏妍表示在拍攝游水戲份前要努力減肥。\n    </div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field--item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4175769/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"丁子朗官仔骨骨上陣。\" class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7613f10a55e40650b8260d2dab2a7a9c/2025-04/0L6A2710.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"img_caption\">\n      丁子朗官仔骨骨上陣。\n    </div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field--item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4175770/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"丁子朗、郭柏妍\" class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0e728812380463dc09d4a865fa559bd5/2025-04/0L6A2716.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"img_caption\">\n      丁子朗、郭柏妍\n    </div>\n</article>\n<p>郭柏妍飾演陳豪妹妹，也是一名游泳運動員，劇情指她在一次比賽中令身體某部分癱瘓，最終離世，她直言在拍攝游水戲份前要努力減肥。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2061994/即時-娛樂-俠醫丨劉佩玥帶病上陣死頂開工-自爆演心機女要色誘陳豪丁子朗-郭柏妍為拍游水戲努力減肥",
