        {
            "title": "俠醫丨陳豪喜見張振朗受力捧 唔介意被指「父女戀」太太keep得太好  獲張曦雯讚按腳手勢好",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"俠醫丨陳豪喜見張振朗受力捧 唔介意被指「父女戀」太太keep得太好  獲張曦雯讚按腳手勢好\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/a470cfc9b1d3f28393e1290f75356514/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250403/_2025040318595344399.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">俠醫丨陳豪喜見張振朗受力捧 唔介意被指「父女戀」太太keep得太好  獲張曦雯讚按腳手勢好</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>陳豪、張曦雯、劉佩玥、郭柏妍等今日（3日）出席無綫新劇《俠醫》開鏡拜神，張曦雯透露劇中最初是陳豪的病人，經常跌倒扭傷，陳豪常為她按腳，大讚陳豪手勢好，按摩很舒服，笑稱男友也未曾為她按摩。陳豪自言也有為太太陳茵媺按摩，又指太太很喜歡按摩，並嫌他按得不夠大力兼不夠持續性。陳豪笑稱現時大仔充當按摩隊長，指揮弟妹為媽媽按摩。\n\n</p><h2>與太太補祝生日</h2>\n<p>談到有網民指他與年紀相差十年的太太似足「父女戀」，陳豪笑說：「我係正常，只係老婆keep得太天仙，令到好似有啲距離，其實唔係。Aimee真係keep得好，我有向佢效法，年紀越大keep得仲好。」陳豪又稱近日拍劇拍到不見天日，未能與太太慶祝生日，稍後會去旅行補祝，囡囡也快將生日，現時要先為囡囡安排生日派對。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"陳豪、張曦雯等出席無綫新劇《俠醫》開鏡拜神。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/afd391737b87829531318ee48fe6df59/2025-04/0L6A2817.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        陳豪、張曦雯等出席無綫新劇《俠醫》開鏡拜神。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"香港著名中醫師黃天賜教授\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3803454ef7d0c7f32f795f5589b96d42/2025-04/0L6A2837.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        香港著名中醫師黃天賜教授\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"張曦雯說劇中最初是陳豪的病人，經常跌倒扭傷，陳豪常為她按腳。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/199241985e983744947dc2a588e8d593/2025-04/0L6A2778.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        張曦雯說劇中最初是陳豪的病人，經常跌倒扭傷，陳豪常為她按腳。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"張曦雯大讚陳豪手勢好！\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/01d6c4bb317795e32a7f831764905a7d/2025-04/0L6A2782.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        張曦雯大讚陳豪手勢好！\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"陳豪近日被指與年紀相差10年的太太似足「父女戀」。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/57edc86965dd0b5dd47ed5491a051bb1/2025-04/0L6A2785.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        陳豪近日被指與年紀相差10年的太太似足「父女戀」。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"陳豪笑說太太Aimee真係keep得好！\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/de8e9c4c52e0d65a78f2549c9721828b/2025-04/0L6A2795.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        陳豪笑說太太Aimee真係keep得好！\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"陳豪因工作太忙，未能與太太慶祝生日，稍後會去旅行補祝。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ce994738e6183297538bceccaadb5bcf/2025-04/0L6A2883.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        陳豪因工作太忙，未能與太太慶祝生日，稍後會去旅行補祝。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"他表示囡囡都即將生日，要先為囡囡安排生日派對。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7cc735155a71fe7bbfda78d6d0e88c5e/2025-04/0L6A2888.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        他表示囡囡都即將生日，要先為囡囡安排生日派對。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"陳豪又說好開心張振朗受公司力捧！\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1daa0a8f5242f9859086a2ef5bdc433c/2025-04/1_1_11.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        陳豪又說好開心張振朗受公司力捧！\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>開心見張振朗得獎</h2>\n<p>另外，對於有指張振朗獲公司力捧取代陳豪，陳豪表示開心見到振朗得獎，他說：「TVB係要讓年輕演員上，唔好話取唔取代，大家都係公司嘅藝人，大家都要靠自己努力做成績畀人睇。」\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
